<bibRefCitation id="BF8E5E046D43E3D680D342973883D838" author="Young, FN" journalOrPublisher="Quaestiones Entomologicae" pageId="24" pageNumber="119" pagination="355 - 381" title="A review of classification of the water beetles of the New World genus Bidessonotus Regimbart (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae: Hydroporinae: Bidessini)." volume="26" year="1990">Young 1990</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
